item.title: CVE-2024-0552|2024-01-15T05:34:49.698Z -- Intumit inc. -- SmartRobot
item.description: Intumit inc. SmartRobot's web framwork has a remote code execution vulnerability. An unauthorized remote attacker can exploit this vulnerability to execute arbitrary commands on the remote server.
